## Common Jinja2 Patterns

### Game Type Filtering

```jinja2
{% set all_game_types = [] %}
{% for game in games %}
    {% if game.game_type %}
        {% for game_type in game.game_type.split(',') %}
            {% set game_type = game_type.strip() %}
            {% if game_type and game_type not in all_game_types %}
                {% set _ = all_game_types.append(game_type) %}
            {% endif %}
        {% endfor %}
    {% endif %}
{% endfor %}
```

### Family Ratings Display

